title: Amazon Launches First Test Satellites for Kuiper Internet Network
description: A United Launch Alliance Atlas V rocket lifts off carrying Amazon's two prototype relay stations for a space-based internet service it calls Project Kuiper, from the Cape Canaveral Space Force Station in Cape Canaveral, Fla., on Oct. 6, 2023. (Joe Skipper/Reuters)
